comment: Thick flavors, heavy on the tounge; corn chowder, vanilla bark, spent matchsticks, and Altoid pepper mints. Like a triple-stamp on a double-stamp!

Rich sweet aroma, maple syrup
Deep wood flavor, absolutely fantastic, then a spice kick on the tail. Good length tail too. 
Medium rich body.
Great. Easy drinking. Smooth. Had it at company party
Pretty smooth with water. Probably a good sipper.
